\c 62
\s Jerusarema rakavandudzwa
\p
\v 1 Nekuda kweZiyoni handinganyarari, uye nekuda kweJerusarema handingazorori, kusvika kururama kwaro kuchibuda sechiedza, neruponeso rwaro semwenje unopfuta.
\v 2 Zvino marudzi achaona kururama kwako, nemadzimambo ose kubwinya kwako; uye uchadanwa nezita idzva, muromo waJehovha warichatumidza.
\v 3 Zvino uchava korona yerunako muruoko rwaJehovha, neukomba hweumambo muruoko rwaMwari wako.
\v 4 Hauchazonzi Musiiwa; nenyika yako haichazonzi Dongo; asi uchanzi Hefizi-Bha, nenyika yako Bheura; nokuti Jehovha anofadzwa newe, nenyika yako ichawanikwa.
\v 5 Nokuti jaya \add sezva\add*rinowana mhandara, \add saizvozvo\add* vanakomana vako vachakuwana; uye muwani \add sezva\add*anofarira mwenga, \add saizvozvo\add* Mwari wako achakufarira.
\p
\v 6 Ndakaisa nharirire pamusoro pemasvingo ako, Jerusarema; zuva rose neusiku hwose havangatongonyarari; imwi vayeudziri vezvaJehovha, regai kunyarara.
\v 7 Uye musamuzorodza, kusvika asimbisa \add izvozvo\add*, uye kusvika aita Jerusarema rive rumbidzo panyika.
\v 8 Jehovha wakapika neruoko rwake rwerudyi uye neruoko rwesimba rake, \add achiti\add*: Zvirokwazvo handichazopi zviyo zvako \add zvive\add* kudya kwevavengi vako, nevanakomana vemutorwa zvirokwazvo havanganwi waini yako itsva yawakatamburira.
\v 9 Asi vakazviunganidza vachazvidya, uye vacharumbidza Jehovha; uye vakaibwerengedza vachainwa pazvivanze zveutsvene hwangu.
\p
\v 10 Pfuurai, pfuurai nemumasuwo, gadzirai nzira yevanhu; simudzai, simudzai mugwagwa mukuru, bvisai mabwe, simudzirai vanhu mureza.
\v 11 Tarirai, Jehovha wakanzwikwa kusvika kumugumo wenyika: Iti kumukunda weZiyoni: Tarira, ruponeso rwako rwunouya; tarira, mubairo wake anawo, uye zvaanoripira zviri pamberi pake.
\v 12 Zvino vachavatumidza \add kuti:\add* Vanhu Vatsvene, Vakadzikunurwa vaJehovha; newe uchatumidzwa \add kuti:\add* Mutsvakwa, Guta risina kusiiwa.